AucaCoyan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11253] fixed markdown formatting on LSP hover
schrieveslaach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11252] upgraded the lsp-server dependency
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11248] added a default for nu lib dirs
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11244] fixed the 
``nu-std``
 README
, 
