 functionality to 
``last``
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11241] upgraded to polars 0.35
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11238] removed unnecessary boxing of 
``Stack::recursion_count``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11213] fixed 
``get -i``
 ignoring errors for only the first cellpath
KAAtheWiseGit 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11235] fixed help for wrapped commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11228] added a special error for calling 
``metadata``
 on $env and $nu
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11130] matched 
``++=``
 capabilities with 
``++``
drbrain made error message improvements: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11230] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11222] 2
