[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11205] fixed 
``Option<&str> == Option<&String>``
 build error when using rust_decimal/rkyv feature
p00f 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11203] exposed argv
[
0
]
 as 
``$env.PROCESS_PATH``
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11202] fixed highlighting of spread subexpressions in records
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11192] reduced code duplication in eval.rs and eval_const.rs
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11183] added an error on 
``use path item1 item2``
, if item1 is not a module
poliorcetics 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10825] added default docs for aliases, generated from the command they point to
